\begin_inset Formula \[
\frac{\partial}{\partial n'}\cos\left(n,s\right)=\frac{\partial}{\partial n'}\frac{\left(Q-P'\right)\cdot n}{s}=\frac{\left(Q-P'\right)\cdot n\frac{\partial s}{\partial n'}-s\frac{\partial}{\partial n'}\left(Q-P'\right)\cdot n}{s^{2}}=\frac{-s\cos\left(n,s\right)\cos\left(s,n'\right)+s\cos\left(n,n'\right)}{s^{2}}\]

